Introduction

Sohee (Korean: 소희; Japanese: ソヒ) is a South Korean singer under Woollim Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group Rocket Punch.

In 2018, she participated in Mnet's survival show Produce 48. She was eliminated in the episode 8 after ranking 43rd place.

On July 23, 2019, Woollim Entertainment released a concept film showing the six members of their new girl group, Rocket Punch, for the first time, with Sohee being one of them. On July 26, her solo concept film was released.

She debuted as a member of Rocket Punch on August 7, 2019 with the mini album Pink Punch.
